{"id":14351,"date":"2025-02-13T16:16:39","date_gmt":"2025-02-13T22:16:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/?page_id=14351"},"modified":"2025-02-13T18:16:58","modified_gmt":"2025-02-14T00:16:58","slug":"youth-apprenticeship","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/youth-apprenticeship\/","title":{"rendered":"Youth Apprenticeship"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"14351\" class=\"elementor elementor-14351\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-bb75921 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"bb75921\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-240e5e2\" data-id=\"240e5e2\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb72640 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bb72640\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Grow Your Workforce -<br> Wisconsin's Youth Apprenticeship Program<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c23132e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c23132e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-size: 1em;\">A<\/span><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); font-size: 1em;\">re you looking for motivated, aspiring professionals to support your business? The\u00a0<\/span><a style=\"font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 1em;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.yawisconsin.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Wisconsin Youth Apprenticeship (YA) Program<\/span><\/a><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); font-size: 1em;\">\u00a0connects employers like you with students eager to gain hands-on experience while contributing to your success.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2a560e66 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2a560e66\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1a68ce3\" data-id=\"1a68ce3\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-64e5979c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"64e5979c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-14352\" title=\"Apprenticeship Image\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Apprenticeship-1024x1024.png\" alt=\"Beaver Dam Apprenticeships - photo of a mentor and a student.\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Apprenticeship-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Apprenticeship-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Apprenticeship-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Apprenticeship-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Apprenticeship.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" \/><\/p>\n<\/figure>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why Partner with Youth Apprenticeship?<\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Develop a Skilled Workforce\u00a0\u2013 Train and mentor students in your industry, shaping the next generation of professionals.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Fill Workforce Gaps\u00a0\u2013 Gain reliable support for your business while cultivating future full-time employees.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Cost-Effective Hiring Solution\u00a0\u2013 Youth apprentices earn wages while learning, providing an affordable way to build your talent pipeline.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Fresh Perspectives &amp; Innovation\u00a0\u2013 Students bring new ideas, energy, and tech-savviness to your organization.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Strengthen Community &amp; Industry\u00a0\u2013 Support local workforce development while enhancing your company\u2019s visibility as a leader in career education.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How The Upgraded YA Portal Makes Hiring Easy:<\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Effortless Job Postings\u00a0\u2013 Quickly list and update apprenticeship opportunities.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.yawisconsin.org\/hiring-inquiry\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Click here to create your account!<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Pre-Screened Candidates\u00a0\u2013 Starting in March, browse and connect with qualified students who are eager to learn.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Streamlined Communication\u00a0\u2013 Message applicants and schedule interviews all in one place.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Getting Started is Simple:<\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Sign Up Today\u00a0\u2013 Receive your personalized portal credentials within 2-3 business days.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Post Your Opportunities\u00a0\u2013 Start showcasing openings to student applicants.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u2705\u00a0Connect with Candidates in March\u00a0\u2013 Review applicants and find the right fit for your team.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Now is the perfect time to invest in the future of your business!\u00a0Join in building a skilled, prepared workforce while gaining valuable support for your company. Need assistance or want more in-depth info? Contact Erin Wierenga at (920) 296-9727 or <a href=\"mailto:ewierenga@cesa6.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>ewierenga@cesa6.org<\/strong><\/a>, and she&#8217;d be happy to meet with you to help get things started for you.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Grow Your Workforce &#8211; Wisconsin&#8217;s Youth Apprenticeship Program Are you looking for motivated, aspiring professionals to support your business? The\u00a0Wisconsin Youth Apprenticeship (YA) Program\u00a0connects employers like you with students eager to gain hands-on experience while contributing to your success. Why Partner with Youth Apprenticeship? \u2705\u00a0Develop a Skilled Workforce\u00a0\u2013 Train and mentor students in your industry, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-14351","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"meta_box":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/14351","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14351"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/14351\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":14363,"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/14351\/revisions\/14363"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14351"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}